                    <div class="lcds-card__body"> 
            <h3 class="lcds-card__title">Counterterrorism and Emerging Threats</h3>
            <p class="lcds-card__text">FDA plays a critical role in protecting the United States from chemical, biological, radiological, nuclear, and emerging infectious disease threats.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </a>
    
